  "detailed_description": "<h1>STEAM DECK</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1976100/extras/aa8bf7fbeaed7155b4ee9e83c6f1b9ff.avif?t=1729019488\" width=600 height=252 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1976100/extras/74445c95ea6a17c42342b96faeea25fa.avif?t=1729019488\" width=600 height=190 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1976100/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.poster.avif?t=1729019488\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1976100/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.webm?t=1729019488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1976100/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.mp4?t=1729019488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>From life to death, our cells face countless battles, annihilating thousands of invading viruses and bacteria. Embark on this incredible journey and unlock new cells, medications, and nanotechnology to strengthen yourself in the greatest adventure a living being can face: life!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1976100/extras/33b8824b887d0e0a65f09e848d31a0b6.poster.avif?t=1729019488\" width=600 height=197 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1976100/extras/33b8824b887d0e0a65f09e848d31a0b6.webm?t=1729019488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>In Survivor Cells, speed is just the beginning to protect your cell from relentless attacks. You'll also need to make strategic decisions by controlling your nanobot and upgrading your medications as you progress. This is a casual and challenging game with elements of roguelite, bullet hell, and tower defense, where survival is the key to victory!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1976100/extras/f295b2c625d02bf75109a6baeb6cfd84.poster.avif?t=1729019488\" width=600 height=197 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1976100/extras/f295b2c625d02bf75109a6baeb6cfd84.webm?t=1729019488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1976100/extras/a2cbb95366a16c85a4e0c1004b6fc2de.webp?t=1729019488\" width=600 height=50 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In Survivor Cells, you:</h2><br>- Will face and defeat bacteria with devastating attacks and unique abilities;<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1976100/extras/552d655d0ad139ddec3129294ced4202.poster.avif?t=1729019488\" width=600 height=197 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1976100/extras/552d655d0ad139ddec3129294ced4202.webm?t=1729019488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>- Advancing in the journey of life unlocks new cells with new special abilities;<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1976100/extras/8f74c22c097aa17a84620b4b5277ca39.poster.avif?t=1729019488\" width=600 height=197 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1976100/extras/8f74c22c097aa17a84620b4b5277ca39.webm?t=1729019488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>- Use nanotechnology and control nanobots to destroy viruses and bacteria;<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1976100/extras/57857b8fad85e29203a6608c942c2a1a.poster.avif?t=1729019488\" width=600 height=197 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1976100/extras/57857b8fad85e29203a6608c942c2a1a.webm?t=1729019488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>- Can use medications to increase your ability to destroy viruses and bolster your defense;<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1976100/extras/b3f4c12b41db52c7804292558c7c5bae.poster.avif?t=1729019488\" width=600 height=197 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1976100/extras/b3f4c12b41db52c7804292558c7c5bae.webm?t=1729019488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>- Face different viruses and bacteria with distinct characteristics and abilities;<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1976100/extras/fb991a90aa84d8c03114e5e35064828b.poster.avif?t=1729019488\" width=600 height=197 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1976100/extras/fb991a90aa84d8c03114e5e35064828b.webm?t=1729019488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>- Face super bacteria \"Boss\" with special abilities;<b